summary:
Simple Ring That adds 500% regeneration to Health,Magicka and Stamina.
Can Be found on the shelf in helgan keep first room
descriptionHtml:
this is my first mod.
after being in an accident that has prevented me from getting work i decided to give modding a go due to bordom.

Simple Ring That adds 500% regeneration to Health,Magicka and Stamina.
Can Be found on the shelf in helgan keep first room

it works with the basic skyrim onwards so anyone can play
